snippet.textDisplay: You have absolutely named these right as "Magical Journey". This one particularly had tears flowing from my eyes. As an Indian, and someone who loves Coke Studio Pakistan, I could kind of feel Xulfi's emotions about such diversity coming together. As a Gujaati person, I was curious to know more about the Gujarati bit in the song and thus came here to watch the journey. But what I found here was so much more and deep. Thank you for creating such amazing music. Xulfi, you are so right on calling music as the bridge jo aapke narrative ko dilon ko badal sakta hai. Dher saara pyaar dikha iss video mein. Main actually ro di aapne yeh jo diversity ikkattha ki thi woh dekhke. Also, the way you all embrace each other with those hugs is so warm.
